                                    <p>Two adjacent fragments of a <material>nummulitic limestone</material> <objectType>base</objectType>, widely mutilated on the left; the blocks are 
                                        finished on all sides; there is a hole on the upper side. On the front face of the left fragments there is a quadrangular recess for the insertion of a panel, perhaps 
                                        resulting from a subsequent reuse.
